data.name: Chunky Guacamole
data.quickTastyDescription: A fresh and creamy avocado dip, perfect for snacking or as a topping for tacos!
detailedCookingInstructions: Cut the avocados in half, remove the pit, and scoop the flesh into a bowl.
Mash the avocado lightly with a fork, leaving some chunks for texture.
Add lime juice, diced tomato, diced red onion, chopped cilantro, salt, black pepper, and garlic powder to the bowl.
Gently mix all ingredients until combined, but still chunky.
Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.
Serve immediately with tortilla chips or as a topping for your favorite dishes.
